org.apache.flink.runtime.clusterframework.types

类 TaskManagerSlot

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.runtime.clusterframework.types.TaskManagerSlot

  • public class TaskManagerSlot
extends java.lang.Object
    A TaskManagerSlot represents a slot located in a TaskManager. It has a unique identification and resource profile associated.
